# Built-in 4K reference templates
# Capture at 3840×2160 (or native 4K).
#
# ── Race templates ──
# start_menu.png        — "START RACE" button on race start screen
# restart_menu.png     — "RESTART" / "RACE AGAIN" on results screen
# creative_hub.png     — Creative Hub menu option
# eventlab.png          — EventLab submenu
# play_event.png        — "Play Event" button
# events_arrow.png     — Events navigation arrow
# my_history.png        — "My History" menu option
# choose_race_type.png — Race type selector
# car_select.png        — Car selection screen
# next_activity.png     — "What's Next" recommended activity screen

# ── Wheel spin templates ──
# my_horizon_tab.png    — "My Horizon" top-nav tab
# super_wheelspin.png   — Super Wheelspin tile (3 wheels)
# normal_wheelspin.png  — Normal Wheelspin tile (1 wheel)
# wheelspin_skip.png    — "SKIP" fast-forward prompt
# wheelspin_collect.png — Prize collect prompt
# wheelspin_collect_final.png — Final spin collect (no more spins)
# wheelspin_duplicate.png — Duplicate car reward screen

# ── Buy templates ──
# collection_log.png    — Collection Journal menu
# discover_japan.png   — Discover Japan / Master Explorer card
# car_collection.png   — Car Collection grid view
# subaru.png           — Subaru brand tile
# 22b_sti.png          — 22B-STi car tile

# ── Mastery grid ──
# See mastery_grid.json for node unlock path
